---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Contact — SageCG Venture Studio"
  description="Get in touch with SageCG — partnerships, press, careers across the portfolio, or just to say hello."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">Contact</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl tracking-tight leading-[1.02]">Say hello.</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-[var(--color-ink)]/75 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      The studio is small and we read everything that comes in. Tell us what you’re working on and we’ll point you to the right person — or write back ourselves.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@sagecg.com"
        class="group block rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-rule)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-ink)]/40 transition-colors"
      >
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">General</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl tracking-tight group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">hello@sagecg.com</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">Partnerships, press, or a friendly note.</p>
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:careers@sagecg.com"
        class="group block rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-rule)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-ink)]/40 transition-colors"
      >
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">Careers</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl tracking-tight group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">careers@sagecg.com</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">Roles across the portfolio companies.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div id="founder" class="mt-16 border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] pt-12 scroll-mt-24">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">Founder</p>
      <div class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-8 gap-y-6 items-start">
        <!-- Portrait placeholder -->
        <div class="h-28 w-28 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-accent)]/20 to-[var(--color-ink)]/10 border border-[var(--color-rule)] flex items-center justify-center font-display text-3xl text-[var(--color-ink)]/70">
          RP
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">Rob Pfleghardt</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">
            Founder &amp; Operator · SageCG
          </p>
          <p class="mt-5 text-[var(--color-ink)]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Rob founded Sage Consulting Group in 1998 and has spent the years since starting, building, and operating companies — first in Oracle E-Business Suite consulting (Sage Consulting Group, Inc., OraTemps LLC, OneTeam Consulting) and now across a focused portfolio of SaaS, EdTech, GovTech, Sports, and Community products.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-ink)]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            He’s an operator-builder by temperament: hands-on with product, deeply involved in design and engineering decisions, and skeptical of anything that can’t earn its keep. SageCG’s seven active companies and apps — and the Labs concepts on the bench — all started from problems he kept watching real people struggle with.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-ink)]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Based in Virginia.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-sm">
            <a
              class="text-[var(--color-ink)]/80 hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] underline underline-offset-4 decoration-[var(--color-rule)] hover:decoration-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors"
              href="mailto:rob@sagecg.com"
            >
              rob@sagecg.com
            </a>
            <a
              class="text-[var(--color-ink)]/80 hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] underline underline-offset-4 decoration-[var(--color-rule)] hover:decoration-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors"
              href="https://github.com/rob637"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
            >
              GitHub →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] pt-8">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">Mailing</p>
      <address class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink)]/80 not-italic">
        Sage Consulting Group · 504 Mashie Drive, Vienna, VA 22180
      </address>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
